For example, below query will run on all indices that start with `test`:

    POST test*/_update_by_query?conflicts=proceed&amp;wait_for_completion=false
    {
          &quot;script&quot; : &quot;ctx._source.A.remove(&#39;B&#39;)&quot;, 
           &quot;query&quot; : {
